Below are some milestones that Samita and I propose. Please provide
comments and suggestions.

January  2014  WG adoption of IPv6-over-foo documents
February 2014  WG review to determine adoption of:
                            1)   6lo MIB document(s)
                            2)   Generic header compression document
                            3)   Backbone Router document
                            4)   draft-thubert-roll-forwarding-frags-01.txt


March    2014 WG last call for adopted IPv6-over-foo I-Ds
April       2014 WG last call for adopted 6lo MIB document

June      2014 First draft of a generic guideline on IPv6-over-foo
                        Review the following drafts :
                        draft-bormann-6lowpan-roadmap-03.txt
                        draft-bormann-intarea-alfi-02.txt

July     2014 IESG submission of IPv6-over-foo and MIB documents
August  2014  WG adoption of  generic guideline/roadmap document
Sept   2014  WG LC for other WG adopted documents
Nov      2014 IESG submission of the other WG adopted documents
Nov      2014 Re-charter

