Two comments on that timeline:

-- I'm not sure all IP-over-foo documents are at the same level of =
advancement.
In particular, DECT-ULE may be a bit behind the others as DECT-ULE is =
still stabilizing.
We probably have to check with the authors to see whether Jan 2014 =
adoption is realistic.

-- GHC has been pretty much stable for a long time, and has already =
received some review in 6LoWPAN. =20
I'm not sure what we are waiting for there.

Gr=FC=DFe, Carsten


