>>  IPv6 over Networks of Resource-constrained Nodes (6lo)
>> ------------------------------------------------
>> Current Status: Proposed WG
>>
>> Chairs:
>>   Ulrich Herberg <ulrich@herberg.name>
>>   Samita Chakrabarti <samita.chakrabarti@ericsson.com>
>>
>> Technical advisors:
>>   Ralph Droms <rdroms.ietf@gmail.com>
>>
